  "body": "<hr />\n<p><a href=\"https://bisecthosting.com/ShiNeaL\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://www.bisecthosting.com/partners/custom-banners/0a1dabb1-e556-40ea-9b7d-4a18d2247121.png\" /></a></p>\n\n<hr />\n<p>╔═══╣DESCRIPTION╠═══╗<br />\nThis pack changes striders to snails. When you saddle and ride them, you use scaffolding to be able to hang on. This was just a mini side pack but I really love the way it looks!<br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>Reviews</p>\n\n<p>Video - <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/shorts/NZwX9cPIS8Y\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Minecraft Snail</a> (2k Views)<br />\nAuthor - <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/CursedMinecraftPolice\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">MineCurse</a> (52.5k Subs)<br />\n<br />\nVideo - <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hE_Ek9EbT0Q\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Steveee&#39;s Content: What you need to know | #StopSteveee</a> (4.7k Views)<br />\nAuthor - <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/c/YokaiS\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">YokaiS</a> (735 Subs)<br />\n<br />\nVideo - <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZiB4sAv1kRU\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">2022 vs 2069 textures</a> (13 Views)<br />\nAuthor - <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCAjnMIQ6Bws23w3ItGwhVZA\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">Cow</a> (Subs Hidden)</p>\n\n<hr />\n<p>╔═══╣CREDITS╠═══╗<br />\nShinyDragon96 - Owner, Textures, Models, Organizer, Publisher<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/816893940594769950/981406621668360202/LinkTree_Block.png\" style=\"height:32px; width:64px\" /> <a href=\"/member/shinydragon96/\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/816893940594769950/981406622301696010/PMC_Block.png\" style=\"height:32px; width:64px\" /></a><a href=\"https://discord.gg/K55Zv3xrUh\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\"> <img src=\"htt